            "text": "Summary"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Continuous monitoring of third-party AI risk converts the TPRM programme from an annual event into a live capability. Four signal categories — API health, security advisories, model changes, and compliance/contractual events — each require dedicated detection mechanisms and triage workflows. Automated tools (health probes, model pin verification, compliance calendars) surface actionable signals; structured escalation paths ensure that the right people receive alerts at the right time. The combined evidence stream feeds the TPRM evidence package for regulatory examination."
          }
        ]
